1
00:00:44,962 --> 00:00:49,634
I'm Mohammad Ali Keshavarz,
the actor who plays the director.

2
00:00:49,967 --> 00:00:52,553
The other actors are all locals.

3
00:00:53,221 --> 00:00:56,557
We're in Koker, about 250 miles -

4
00:00:56,682 --> 00:00:59,644
no, 220 miles north of Tehran,

5
00:00:59,769 --> 00:01:03,064
where an earthquake
destroyed everything last year.

6
00:01:03,231 --> 00:01:06,776
Sir, the girls are hungry
and have a long way to go.

7
00:01:06,901 --> 00:01:08,778
Could we speed it up?

8
00:01:08,986 --> 00:01:11,739
We've come to this rebuilt school

9
00:01:11,989 --> 00:01:14,242
to choose a young actress.

10
00:01:19,497 --> 00:01:22,625
Sorry it's taking so long.

11
00:01:34,387 --> 00:01:36,764
What's your name?
- Mehri Ziai.

12
00:01:38,391 --> 00:01:40,768
- And yours?
- Sima Ali Mohammadi.

13
00:01:40,935 --> 00:01:43,104
- What?
- Sima Ali Mohammadi.

14
00:01:44,105 --> 00:01:46,440
- And yours?
- Leyla Naghipour.

15
00:01:48,609 --> 00:01:51,404
- Your name?
- Tahereh Ladanian.

16
00:01:51,612 --> 00:01:54,282
Mrs. Shiva,
take down this girl's address.

17
00:01:54,448 --> 00:01:57,618
Your address?
- Near the Lakeh bazaar.

18
00:01:57,743 --> 00:02:00,621
- Your name?
- Tahereh Ladanian.

19
00:02:01,330 --> 00:02:03,749
- Your address?
- Near the Lakeh bazaar.

20
00:02:03,874 --> 00:02:06,961
- What's your name?
- Fariba Jafari.

21
00:02:08,087 --> 00:02:10,423
- What year?
- Third year, literature.

22
00:02:10,548 --> 00:02:13,009
Mrs. Shiva, get her name too.

23
00:02:13,217 --> 00:02:14,969
Tell me your name...

24
00:02:15,177 --> 00:02:17,346
- And you?
- Nazila Khadem.

25
00:02:17,471 --> 00:02:19,140
Mrs. Shiva, get her name.

26
00:02:19,348 --> 00:02:20,808
Your address?

27
00:02:20,975 --> 00:02:22,893
I don't have an exact address.

28
00:02:23,019 --> 00:02:25,062
But where do you live?

29
00:02:25,187 --> 00:02:27,481
Rostamabad, in Jalaliyeh.

30
00:02:30,401 --> 00:02:32,153
What's your name?

31
00:02:32,278 --> 00:02:33,988
Zeynab Hassanpour.

32
00:02:36,991 --> 00:02:39,076
Stay in your lines.

33
00:02:39,201 --> 00:02:41,495
Sir, will you show this film?

34
00:02:41,620 --> 00:02:45,082
What's it matter to us if you film us...

35
00:02:45,333 --> 00:02:47,501
but don't show it anywhere?

36
00:02:47,710 --> 00:02:49,670
- You mean on TV?
- Yes.

37
00:02:49,837 --> 00:02:50,963
You're right.

38
00:02:51,380 --> 00:02:53,674
But is that any reason not to film?

39
00:02:53,841 --> 00:02:55,843
At least show it to us.

40
00:02:56,010 --> 00:02:58,179
Your last film was on Channel 2.

41
00:02:58,346 --> 00:03:01,015
We don't get that here.
Why bother?

42
00:03:01,140 --> 00:03:03,851
What do you girls say?
Should we film or not?

43
00:03:03,976 --> 00:03:05,770
Film!

44
00:03:06,020 --> 00:03:07,897
But you have to show it!

45
00:03:08,522 --> 00:03:10,441
You have to show it!

46
00:03:10,649 --> 00:03:12,860
- What's your name?
- Tahereh.

47
00:03:13,110 --> 00:03:14,862
- Tahereh what?
- Poursadeghi.

48
00:03:15,905 --> 00:03:19,116
Mrs. Shiva, get her name too.

49
00:03:27,083 --> 00:03:29,668
- What's your name?
- Zahra Jenab.

50
00:03:29,877 --> 00:03:31,670
- From where?
- Rostamabad.

51
00:03:31,796 --> 00:03:34,256
- How old are you?
- Fifteen.

52
00:03:35,341 --> 00:03:37,885
Mrs. Shiva, get her name.

53
00:03:38,010 --> 00:03:39,887
- Your name?
- Zahra Jenab.

54
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:49,230
- Address?
- Rostamabad, in Koker.

