Hossein, you forgot this.

1265
01:24:32,568 --> 01:24:33,736
Cut!

1266
01:24:33,903 --> 01:24:35,863
Tahereh, you said “Hossein” again.

1267
01:24:35,988 --> 01:24:39,158
I told you:
You have to say “Mr. Hossein.”

1268
01:24:39,909 --> 01:24:40,910
Take 5.

